headline: Will New Cloud and AI Alliances Reshape S&P Global's (SPGI) Data Distribution Narrative?
summary: S&P Global recently priced and completed a US$1.00 billion dual-tranche senior notes offering and announced new AI data integrations with Amazon Web Services, while also entering a multi-year partnership with Google Cloud to modernize data distribution and workflow automation. Together, these moves highlight how S&P Global is pairing long-term funding with cloud and AI alliances to deepen the reach and utility of its proprietary data across financial, energy, and supply chain...

headline: Energy Companies from Around the World Win Honors at S&P Global Energy's 27th Annual Platts Global Energy Awards
summary: S&P Global Energy (formerly S&P Global Commodity Insights), the leading global independent provider of data, insights, analysis, and benchmark prices for the commodities and energy expansion markets, tonight honored industry excellence in 21 performance categories and winners from across the globe at the Platts Global Energy Awards gala held at the Casa Cipriani South Street in downtown New York City.
